source: A cursed blade, forged by the ancient smiths of the Sorr-Akkath in the forges of Tirmar and blessed by Sorr-Tarr.
Zealots can transmit a powerful electrical discharge with their antennae.
Pilgrims can spray a target with a pheromone that burns the skin and makes its allies frenzied.
Giant beetles can spit a short cloud of acid with their mouth.
